  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan <br /><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> YoRHa Clan, Level 16+ <br />Now having explored and gained knowledge of nearly everything you could in life, you can prepare for the end without any weight upon what you call a \"heart\". You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li>While you are outnumbered in intiative, you gain advantage on all attack rolls, skill checks, and saving throws you make so long as you are not restrained or grappled.</li><li>You can pay the cost of jutsu with hit points in place of chakra, at a rate of 4 hit points to 1 chakra. Hit points lost in this way cannot be regained until you complete a rest of any type.</li><li>When you die, you can choose to become a memory that lives on within creatures allied to you. A number of creatures that knew you in life equal to your proficiency bonus gain access to one of your jutsu, features, feats, or traits permanently.</li></ul>",
